ng%20and%2For%20intra-group%20financing%20activities\"><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:#1155CC;\'>https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/WP/Issues/2020/11/26/International-Taxation-and-Luxembourgs-Economy-49879#:~:text=Luxembourg%20receives%20ample%20investment%20from%20multinational%20corporations%2C%20in,via%20companies%20performing%20holding%20and%2For%20intra-group%20financing%20activities</span></a></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;line-height:200%;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;\'><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\'>De Leon, D. &nbsp;(2022, July 22). TRACKER: Candidates who spent the most in 2022, based on their SOCEs. <em>Rappler</em>.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.rappler.com/newsbreak/tracker-candidates-spent-most-statement-contributions-expenditures-2022/\"><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:#1155CC;\'>https://www.rappler.com/newsbreak/tracker-candidates-spent-most-statement-contributions-expenditures-2022/</span></a></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;line-height:200%;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\'>Limpot, K.<em>&nbsp;(2021, February 14). Explainer: What you need to know about the PDAF scam. CNN.</em></span><a href=\"https://www.cnnphilippines.com/news/2021/2/14/PDAF-scam-what-you-need-to-know.html\"><em><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;\'>&nbsp;</span></em></a><a href=\"https://www.cnnphilippines.com/news/2021/2/14/PDAF-scam-what-you-need-to-know.html\"><em><span style=\'font-size:16px;line-height:200%;f